    <briefdescription>
<para>Status codes returned by hipDNN backend API functions. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This file defines the status codes used throughout the hipDNN backend API. All hipDNN backend functions return a hipdnnStatus_t value to indicate success or the type of error that occurred. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
